      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON DEUTZ (1) has some solid form under her belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 23.20 beating Jaja Ding Dong. Yet to miss the placings from three starts out of this box. Can measure up again. COSTLY HABITS (5) finds it hard to win. Finished second (17.94) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Can measure up. HAYDEN'S MILK (2) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a 0.8 lengths third (23.00) in a Other at Gawler. Speedy beginner who should be in the action early from an inside box. Key player on best and worth another try. LEKTRA EDGE (8) deserves plenty of thought at his first run at this distance.",
